#

Chipotle Black Bean Burger

30 min
$8
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Egg

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyQuickHealthy

Description

A smoky, spicy black bean burger with a delightful crunch and savory flavor.

Ingredients

  • canned black beans: 1 can (15 oz)
  • breadcrumbs: 1/2 cup
  • cornmeal: 1/4 cup
  • egg: 1 large
  • green bell pepper: 1/2, chopped
  • red onion: 1/4, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • chipotle sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • pepper: 1/4 teaspoon
  • olive oil: for frying
  • burger buns: 2
  • lettuce: 2 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • avocado: 1/2, sliced
